main_body:
Regulation (EC) No 1509/2003 is amended as follows:
1. the title is replaced by the following:
"Commission Regulation (EC) No 1509/2003 of 27 August 2003 opening a standing invitation to tender for the resale on the Community market of barley held by the German intervention agency.";
2. in Article 1(1), "82500 tonnes" is replaced by "136000 tonnes";
3. Annex I is replaced by the text in the Annex to this Regulation;
4. in the title of Annex II, "82500 tonnes" is replaced by "136000 tonnes".
